HEADWORD: Stockish
<hw>Stock"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a stock; stupid;
blockish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Since naught so <qex>stockish</qex>, hard, and full of rage,⟦br⟧
But music for the time doth change his nature.</q>
